<h2>Step 6: Prioritize Keywords by Business Value</h2>
<p>You now have a list of keywords organized into clusters. The question is: which ones do you write first?</p>
<p><strong>Score each keyword on 3 factors:</strong></p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
